title: OUTREACH
description: The Outreach Ministry, committed to surpassing our church walls, is a symbol of compassion, seeking to cater to the physical needs of people while also addressing their emotional and spiritual well-being.

title: KIDS & JUNIOR YOUTH
description: Kids and Jr. Youth Ministry is dedicated to developing a deep relationship with God's Word from a young age. Our commitment is to provide the kids with the necessary tools to navigate life, based on faith, love, and a commitment to goodwill.
